<h3 id="setup">Setup</h3>

<p>There is a <a href="https://github.com/tsjensen/fuse-core/wiki/Setup-Instructions">simple setup guide</a> which lets you get
a <em>Fuse Core</em> based website up and running for free with no web development knowledge.<br />
If you are a web developer, you may be glad to find that <em>Fuse Core</em> has SASS styling and is pretty crisp.</p>

